# --- resumable local VLM shards ---
# Keep only the promoted discovery/evaluation artifacts below. Interrupted
# shards, retries, and prompt experiments stay local and are summarized under
# research/results/ instead of appearing as unreviewed data additions.
data/*_vllm_*.jsonl
data/*_vllm_*.jsonl.meta.json
